Source: krapplet
Maintainer: Johannes Willem (Hans) Fernhout <hfern@fernhout.info>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-python, python3-setuptools, python3-all
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: krapplet
Architecture: all
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://gitlab.com/hfernh/krapplet
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-secretstorage, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0 
Description: Graphical password manager based on gnome-keyring.
 Krapplet is a graphical password manager which relies on gnome-keyring for storing secrets
 (passwords) and other information. It is developed as a Linux system tray icon applet, and 
 aims to not be in the user's way.
